# usr/

User-facing documentation for the Intent system, providing task-oriented guides, comprehensive references, and deployment instructions for end users and developers.

## Files

- `user_guide.md` -- Task-oriented guide for using Intent, including installation, getting started, working with steel threads, documentation management, and LLM collaboration
- `reference_guide.md` -- Comprehensive reference covering all Intent commands, document templates, directory structure, configuration options, best practices, and terminology
- `deployment_guide.md` -- Deployment instructions for installing Intent globally or per-project, with configuration, integration, maintenance, and troubleshooting guidance
